B-17 Gunner: Air War Over Germany hands you all the white-knuckle action that it is to man a gun positions on the famed "Flying Fortress." Your reactions have to be fast, your judgement flawless and your aim dead-on...you&#039;ve got more than just the other nine men on the plane counting on you...your country is counting on you!

Man any of six gun positions, plus take control of the sights on the daring bomb run itself! Wave after wave of enemy fighters is out to keep your from your appointed target, so you&#039;ll have to blast your way through all of them to keep your formation aloft and rack up the highest score possible.

Do you have what it takes to make it through all 25 missions?
